<li id="cite_note-75"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-75">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">"Suffrage" in Paul S. Boyer and Melvyn Dubofsky, <i>The Oxford companion to United States history</i> (2001) p. 754</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
